metadata.name: enumerate_swf_4
metadata.description: Tests ENUMERATE opcode (0x46) - enumerates object property names with full ECMA-262 compliance. Implements prototype chain walking via __proto__, DontEnum filtering via property flags, and proper shadowing of inherited properties.

what_works: Property shadowing (child properties override prototype properties)
Null terminator handling (pushes undefined to mark end)
Empty object handling (returns only null terminator)
Non-object handling (returns only null terminator for strings, numbers, undefined variables)
Property name ordering (reverse order push for forward order pop)
ecma_262_compliance: Prototype chain enumeration per ECMA-262 Section 12.6.4
DontEnum attribute support per ECMA-262 Section 8.6.1
Duplicate property name prevention across prototype levels
no_graphics_notes: Slash-path/dot-path variable resolution (e.g., '/root/clip' or '_parent.clip') is a MovieClip/timeline feature not applicable in NO_GRAPHICS mode
This feature is part of the variable resolution system, not the ENUMERATE opcode itself
